{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "第十六回\"重回岛上\"讲述了陆小凤独自返回神秘孤岛的经历。他离开老狐狸的船，独自划着小艇在海上漂浮，寻找传说中的暖流。在漂浮过程中，他思念着沙曼，怀疑自己是否爱上了她。到达岛上后，他在海滩上思考珠宝失窃案的真相，推断出小老头是主谋，宫九是执行者。他推断崔诚是被\"隐形人\"所杀，决心去找小老头寻求答案。第二天清晨，陆小凤在岛上与小老头相遇，两人展开了一场关于珠宝失窃案、崔诚之死以及接班人问题的深入对话。小老头承认自己策划了珠宝劫案，但珠宝和人已不在岛上，宫九另有打算。小老头希望陆小凤能成为他的接班人，但陆小凤婉言谢绝。关于崔诚的死因，小老头提及\"隐形人\"的概念，但未给出明确答案。本章通过陆小凤与小老头的对话，逐步揭示了珠宝失窃案的更多细节，同时展现了两人之间的心理博弈。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "静得可以听到花开草长的声音，是吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "你的出现，总是那么突如其来？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你上次在这个岛上看到的事，你认为很怪异？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "怪异极了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这个岛是不是很神秘？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "神秘极了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我是这个岛上的主人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "所以你理所当然的透着神秘？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "一点不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "你知道我这次重回岛上，有什么目的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我当然知道，你有很多疑问，需要我给你答案。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "你会给我答案吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你看呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "以你的武功，以你的智慧，你根本不必隐瞒任何事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你说得很对，只是我却另外有一个希望。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "什么希望？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我希望你是回来告诉我一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你愿意加入我这一行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "我只有让你失望了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为你是一个人回来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "如果你要加入我这一行，你就会带着沙曼回来。可是你并没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我希望我的失望是暂时的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "对于你的希望，我很抱歉不能给你任何诺言。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "你又知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为你不是别人，你是陆小凤。陆小凤是最重诺言的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你能够逃过宫九在船上的攻击，我相信，你的智慧，绝对比我高，我相信，你对于那批珠宝失窃的事，一定想出了很多线索。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "我只知道一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哪一件？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "窃案是你策划的，珠宝和失踪的人都在岛上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你说对了一半。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "哪一半？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "前面的一半。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "你是说，珠宝和人已经不在岛上？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "宫九已经把珠宝和人运回去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "人，宫九另有打算。珠宝，总是要花掉的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "他一个人怎么花？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不是一个人，是很多人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "怪不得这里的人一个也不剩，原来他们都去花这笔钱去了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以，我心目中理想的接班人，只有一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "为什么只有我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为他们都不能甘于寂寞。大吃大喝大玩大闹的人，是很容易被人控制的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "对你来说，这不是很理想吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是很理想，只是，我也就很寂寞了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "因为你找不到接你的班，做领导的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以，我很喜欢你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你对这件窃案，有什么疑问？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "以你们的人力和武功，我知道，要窃去这批珠宝，是轻而易举的事。所以，我只有一个问题想不透。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哪一个问？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "崔诚的死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "小老头",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "记得我对你说过的隐形人吗？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "我的意思是，杀崔诚的人，是怎么隐形的？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    }
  ],
